body_html: Thank you @hughperkins, but I think I had tried the computecpp yesterday, and it's seem that the macbook system is still not supported with computecpp. So, maybe keep waiting for new updates is the only thing I can do (T.T). BTW, my Iris 6100 is eight generation, which is good for OpenCL 1.2.
